<table border="0" cellpadding="2" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td colspan="1" valign="top" align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="5" color="black">
    Selo`s Accelerando</font></td>
    <td colspan="2" valign="top" align="left"><font color="black"><img
    src="http://205.229.72.28/ev1/public_html/images/magic.gif" width="216" height="30" align="right"></font></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td colspan = "3">
    <!--<a href="magic.asp?mode=updateform&amp;ID=93">-->
    <a href="../UserUpdate.asp?ID=93">
    <small><font color="#000080" face="Verdana"><strong>Add New Info Here</strong></font></small>
    </a>
    </td>
    
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
    <font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
    <b>Description:</b> <br>
       The increased speed is directly proportional to one's skill in singing and percussion. It's difficult to quantify the speed increase this spell gives. However, initially it seems to increases movement pace about 10%-15% while singing. And if a hand drum is played, the movement is increased about 15%-25%.<BR>
   Greater percussion skill yields greater speed, such that a percussion skill of 55 increases your speed by nearly %50, and at much higher levels there the increase is closer to 100%.<BR>
<BR>
<B>Location:</B> Any Bard Guild<BR>
<B>Skill:</B> Percussion<BR><br>
    <b>Effects:</b><br>
    Group: Increased Movement & Fatigue
    </font>
    
    </td>
    <td rowspan="2" valign="top" align="right"><font
    face="verdana" color="black" size="1">
    
			&nbsp;<br>
			&nbsp;<br>
			Mana:<br>
			Casting Time:<br>
			Target Type:<br>
			Level:<br>
			Rank:<br>
    </font></td>
    <td rowspan="2" valign="top" align="right"><font
    face="verdana" color="black" size="1">

		  &nbsp;<br>
		  &nbsp;<br>
			0<br>
			3<br>
			Group<br>
			5<br>
			1<br>
    </font></td>
  </tr>
