				To give an idea of your speed by just singing it, you can run as fast as lions or griffons.  As long as you started running &amp; singing the song a few steps ahead of the beast you can stay out of harms way.  Just hope that the direction you choose to run goes to a zone or a guard.  Everytime you try to turn, even to avoid a tree, they can inch closer and closer to you.
