				This song is killer when you juggle it with the Boastful Bellow song. I used it when I was attacked by ghouls then as I was runnin, I'd hit them with the song for about 8pts of damange.  You'll miss a number of times but it's definitly good to wear down higher level guys. Too high and the target will resist. I would stand back, cast Bellow on a target, switch to Selo (MAYBE use instrument because I might be able to outrun them w/out one which defeats the purpose) and have them follow me a bit. I would switch back after their health dropped to half or so.  Doing this technique is definitly time consuming and dangerous.  Best in open areas like West Commons where you can run around not be trapped in enclosed areas.  If your're really good, you can juggle this song, Bellow's and Wistling Warsong for added AC in case they can still hit ya.
