				this song is realy realy useful i think it will be one of the songs that i ALWAYS have memed. you can put inventory slots in the hotkey spaces on the left of your screen. just put your 2 melee weapon slots and 1 inventory slot there (2 if your using a shield) and you can switch from weapon to drums in a hurry. i have used this tactic to save my skin on many occasions. on the island in eruds xing you can out run monsters with this if they team up on you (or your just losing horribly cause that blue con got realy lucky) and just run around the island till the boat comes sure you might have every kerra spider on the island chasing you but who cares youll live. once the boat arrives just hop on for a few seconds stuff will stop chasing you and you can get off of the boat safe and sound.
